LeftPanel - Class in view
In LeftPanel are displayed all the options concerning routines and escs, using three combo box and a button.
LeftPanel(Controller) - Constructor for class view.LeftPanel
Instantiate a LeftPanel which operates using the Controller passed as a parameter.
loadFrom(File...) - Static method in class routine.RoutineLoader
Loads all the routines files (.rou) from the directories specified as parameters, the routines that were parsed correctly can be found with RoutineLoader.getRoutines().
loadParameters() - Method in class analyzer.Analyzer
Loads the parameters from the file specified in the constructor into the Analyzer.parametersRequired map.
